title: Fire, Rescue & EMS Locations in Brunswick County, North Carolina
info:
This map shows the distribution of all Fire, Rescue & EMS Department Station locations in Brunswick County, North Carolina.  This data was developed by researching the Brunswick County Website for list of Fire Departments.
    and this was crossed referrenced with the North Carolina Fire Station Mapping Project. Locations were also confirmed via searching Google Maps..
author: Sean Stewart
